<h2 id="answer">Answer</h2>

<p>Option d is correct.</p>

<p>From the documentation:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Unattended robots should be used for complex and repetitive tasks, especially when structured rules can be used to evaluate conditions</p>
</blockquote>

<p>This covers exam objection 1.2,  how to identify and describe attended vs. unattended UiPath robots</p>

<p>More <a href="https://docs.uipath.com/orchestrator/docs/attended-vs-unattended-automation">details</a> on the difference between attended vs unattended robots can be found in the UiPath documentation.</p>

